Dia. 01 If White Plays
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It looks a bit more difficult, isn't it?
\par It is just because there are more stones, actually it is an easy problem.
\par
\par Let's check if White plays first.
\par White saves his stones with 1, but it doesn't increase his territory. This is also counted with \cf1\b simple counting method\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
