Dia. 02 7 Points?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black plays first the situation is different. Black makes many points.
\par
\par After Black 1 how many points Black's territory has increased by?
\par
\par Black has captured White three \'a1\'e2 stones which is 6 points and there is one more point at X, so it is 7 points, isn't it?
\par
\par Actually it isn't.
\par
\par }
