Dia. 03 Correct Answer is 8 Points
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is easy to forget about points like X and Y.
\par It is obvious that Black made 6 points by capturing the 3 stones, but X is a point, and Y becomes point as well.
\par
\par Therefore Black 1 is worth \cf1\b 8 points\cf0\b0  (White 1 at \b Dia. 01\b0  is same).
\par
\par
\par }
